OL,3,CMeet Ameca: The world's most advanced
OL,4,Chumanoid robot
OL,6,FITV News Scotland Reporter Louise
OL,7,FScott meets Ameca, a humanoid robot
OL,8,Fthat has been designed to look and act
OL,9,Fin a similar way to humans
OL,11,FThe world's most advanced humanoid
OL,12,Frobot has moved in to its first UK
OL,13,Fhome in Edinburgh.
OL,15,FDesigned to look and act like a human,
OL,16,FAmeca is hoping to break down barriers
OL,17,Fand build trust between humans and
OL,18,Frobots.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
