OL,3,CMeet Ameca: The world's most advanced
OL,4,Chumanoid robot
OL,6,FThe National Robotarium on the
OL,7,Foutskirts of Edinburgh is the UK's
OL,8,Fcentre for Robotics and Artificial
OL,9,FIntelligence.
OL,11,FIts Chief Operating Officer Steve
OL,12,FMaclaren said Ameca's arrival "marks a
OL,13,Fsignificant step forward in our
OL,14,Fmission to make robotics more
OL,15,Faccessible and relatable to the people
OL,16,Fof Scotland, the UK and beyond".
OL,18,FWe visited the centre as the first
OL,19,Fgroup of school children met Ameca,
OL,20,Fand they were certainly shocked by
OL,21,Fjust how realistic she was.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
