OL,3,CMeet Ameca: The world's most advanced
OL,4,Chumanoid robot
OL,6,FSome said she was a little creepy, as
OL,7,Fher eyes followed them around the room.
OL,9,FAlongside her human like features,
OL,10,Fartificial intelligence (AI) helps
OL,11,FAmeca to have conversations rather
OL,12,Fthan just answer questions.
OL,14,FAnd she was tested straight away when
OL,15,Fasked "whether she questioned her
OL,16,Fexistence in this state of reality".
OL,18,F'You don't think that, that (Ameca)
OL,19,Fcan actually speak to you' -
OL,20,FSchoolchildren react to their
OL,21,Fexchanges with the robot
