OL,3,CMeet Ameca: The world's most advanced
OL,4,Chumanoid robot
OL,6,FAmeca is the culmination of 15 years
OL,7,Fwork by developers Engineered Arts.
OL,9,FWatch Ameca's response when asked: 'Do
OL,10,Fyou want to take over the world?'
OL,12,FIts founder and CEO Will Jackson said:
OL,13,F"We are incredibly proud to have Ameca
OL,14,Fjoin the many pre-eminent robots at
OL,15,Fthe National Robotarium.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
