OL,3,CMeet Ameca: The world's most advanced
OL,4,Chumanoid robot
OL,6,F"Meeting an AI-embodied humanoid robot
OL,7,Fis a unique experience that very few
OL,8,Fpeople have witnessed and we are very
OL,9,Fexcited to be able to share what can
OL,10,Fbe a profound moment with a wider
OL,11,Faudience."
OL,13,FFor now, Ameca is purely for
OL,14,Feducational purposes, and will be
OL,15,Fgetting out and about at public
OL,16,Fevents, school visits and workshops.
OL,18,FThe most important question of the
OL,19,Fday, of course, was whether Ameca was
OL,20,Fwanting to take over the world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
